15
00:06:28,819 --> 00:06:32,937
<i>... have already gone</i>

16
00:06:39,708 --> 00:06:44,498
<i>For years I've wanted to find time
to write, or keep a diary.</i>

17
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:48,112
<i>Have I anything to say?</i>

18
00:08:00,063 --> 00:08:01,382
<i>Everything's the same.</i>

19
00:08:09,242 --> 00:08:10,277
<i>All the same.</i>

20
00:08:12,538 --> 00:08:16,326
<i>Suddenly it looks like a set,
