23
00:08:32,105 --> 00:08:36,496
<i>No imperial eagle, but where's the
dove Picasso was going to send?</i>

24
00:08:38,071 --> 00:08:40,744
<i>Iùs comfortable to be a communist
millionaire in Paris.</i>

25
00:08:46,708 --> 00:08:50,018
<i>"This humanity has spoken 'enough'
