201
00:25:34,652 --> 00:25:36,483
<i>Death by starvation, by sickness...</i>

202
00:25:36,905 --> 00:25:39,817
<i>... by torture, by frustration.</i>

203
00:26:08,780 --> 00:26:11,738
<i>She cleans the apartment
three times a week.</i>

204
00:26:12,618 --> 00:26:15,576
<i>She's been coming for a year
