01:27:03,314 --> 01:27:07,512
<i>A happy ending, as they say.
Justice triumphed for once.</i>

686
01:27:09,155 --> 01:27:10,952
<i>But is that so?</i>

687
01:27:11,908 --> 01:27:15,947
<i>I'm left in a bad situation;
I'm too educated to be innocent.</i>

688
01:27:16,539 --> 01:27:19,497
<i>They're too ignorant to be guilty.</i>

689
01:27:20,461 --> 01:27:23,578
<i>I just hope they haven't
locked her away.</i>

