699
01:28:12,779 --> 01:28:14,735
THE THOUGHTS OF MAO TSE-TUNG

700
01:28:15,032 --> 01:28:18,991
<i>Attempting to resolve ideological
problems, rights or wrongs...</i>

701
01:28:19,371 --> 01:28:22,124
<i>... by administration or repression,
is not only useless, but harmful.</i>

702
01:28:22,584 --> 01:28:26,782
<i>For the safety of customers who
come to the shop below...</i>

703
01:28:27,215 --> 01:28:30,491
<i>...as well as for the sake of
the tenants...</i>

704
01:28:30,845 --> 01:28:33,484
<i>... why doesn't somebody
repair our balcony?</i>

705
01:28:33,807 --> 01:28:36,799
<i>Seven times I've reported it
to the authorities.</i>

706
01:28:55,961 --> 01:29:00,591
<i>She brought me a stack of photos
taken at her baptism.</i>

707
01:29:07,184 --> 01:29:10,142
<i>It wasn't at all as I imagined.</i>

708
01:29:10,814 --> 01:29:13,692
<i>The robe didn't cling to her body.
There were many people.</i>

709
01:29:16,571 --> 01:29:21,520
<i>I hadn't thought of them, the
witnesses who are everywhere.</i>

710
01:30:41,766 --> 01:30:46,760
<i>People are ready to die, without
considering who's to blame.</i>

711
01:31:04,504 --> 01:31:06,142
<i>What if it all starts?</i>

712
01:31:10,721 --> 01:31:12,439
<i>No good protesting. I'd die, too.</i>

713
01:31:14,893 --> 01:31:17,168
<i>This island is a trap.</i>

714
01:31:18,147 --> 01:31:19,785
<i>We're small, and too poor.</i>

715
01:31:21,568 --> 01:31:23,320
<i>Iùs an expensive dignity.</i>

716
01:31:23,738 --> 01:31:29,290
We definitely reject any intention
of an enquiry...

717
01:31:30,956 --> 01:31:32,753
...any inspection of our country.

718
01:31:34,168 --> 01:31:35,920
Nobody inspects our country.

719
01:31:37,214 --> 01:31:39,011
We know what we're doing.

720
01:31:39,300 --> 01:31:44,090
We know how to defend our integrity
and our independence.

721
01:31:44,849 --> 01:31:49,718
They threaten us with talk of
a nuclear attack.

722
01:31:50,773 --> 01:31:52,570
That doesn't scare us.

723
01:31:53,276 --> 01:31:55,232
We know the age we live in...

724
01:31:55,613 --> 01:31:59,162
...and we must learn how to live
in it, with dignity.

725
01:31:59,785 --> 01:32:02,743
All of us, men and women...

726
01:32:03,123 --> 01:32:07,082
we are all one!

727
01:32:07,462 --> 01:32:09,100
In this hour of danger...

728
01:32:09,965 --> 01:32:14,675
...every one of us, revolutionaries
and patriots...

729
01:32:15,430 --> 01:32:18,069
...share the same peril...

730
01:32:18,768 --> 01:32:21,885
...and victory shall be for all.

731
01:32:22,231 --> 01:32:24,142
Our country or death! We shall win!

